Tutu Tuesday with Short Stack at 7:15 + G
Dustin went
Whooaaaaaaa nellie! It's that terrific time of the year once again, where we don our finest dusty duds, slap some tutus on it, make our asses more colorful than a baboon's and shake those tail-feathers. Join us, from 2pm-2am, on Tu-Tuesday at Short Stack. We're located at 7:15 & G (just off the 7:30 Plaza). Look for the big astroturf lawn and colorful fabrics billowing above. If this was Chicago in 1871, we would say it's gonna be a real Barn Burner. But guess what... is Chicago? IS NOT CHICAGO. No, this is Black Rock City, and we're gonna celebrate our own brand of Bodacious Bouncy Beats and Bonkers Bass Burner. You've gotta feel it to believe it. We'll dance all day and night. Our sister camp Om Skillet will be grilling up their delicious gourmet grilled cheese sandwiches for the first couple hours of the party, so come early to get claim your culinary reward and get cheesy! Check out our official Radio Advertisement!!!! https://soundcloud.com/ninamehta/tutu-tuesday-short-stack ==================================== The Terrifically Titillating Twirly Tutu Tuesday Tunemakers ==================================== Jordy [Short Stack / SF] https://soundcloud.com/curiousjordy Mightykat [Pronto Musique / MONTREAL] https://soundcloud.com/mightykat Manju Masi (Atish + Mark Slee) [Short Stack, Listed, House-Heads / SF] https://soundcloud.com/atish https://soundcloud.com/mcslee Nico Stojan [Dantze, Bar 25 / BERLIN] + Uone [Beef, Chamelon / AUS] https://soundcloud.com/nicostojan https://soundcloud.com/uone Jonathan Will [Pink Mammoth / SF] https://soundcloud.com/jonathan-w Mike Khoury [All Day I Dream, Listed / NYC] + Naveen G [Listed / NYC] https://soundcloud.com/mikekhoury https://soundcloud.com/naveen-g Greenbank [Cityfox / ZURICH] https://soundcloud.com/cityfox Dan Sherman [Short Stack, Qool / SF] + Alex Blackstock [Short Stack, Less Is More / SF] https://soundcloud.com/djdansherman https://soundcloud.com/asblackstock

Silent Dance Party
Dustin went
To receive the soundtrack and location, sign up at: http://www.silentdanceparty.info Join us this summer for a silent dance party, i.e. all of us simultaneously pressing Play to launch the same playlist in our headphones, silent to innocent bystanders. Soundtrack and further details withheld until 24 hours in advance, but you come with: 1) headphones and something that plays music 2) your best 90s outfit and we promise: 1) the greatest 90s hits 2) a ridiculous amount of fun Friends and friends of friends are welcome! -SAN FRANCISCO- Date: Friday, June 17th, 2011 Time: 8:00pm - 10:30pm PST -NEW YORK CITY- Date: Saturday, June 18th, 2011 Time: 8:00pm - 10:30pm EST -LOS ANGELES- Date: Saturday, June 18th, 2011 Time: 5:00pm - 7:30pm PST
